{"tid":491931,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"吵架後發洩性慾！　男脫衣「綑綁雙手」性侵老婆挨告了","createTime":"2017-12-07T04:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:18:49.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d5d712e656e3ae4fe6b542a8323054b9a67b41","tid":491931,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"桃園市一對夫妻平時大小口角不斷，先生在今年5月一天爭執後，突然性慾大發，不管妻子的反抗，強行脫下衣褲，並且拿衣服綑綁住雙手，多次性侵得逞。事後，老婆不滿提告，但最後卻又心軟撤告，最終予以不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n根據《聯合報》報導，夫妻倆今年5月某天凌晨2時許發生爭執，老公突然把老婆往床上扯，甚至壓制住雙手，並且脫去內衣褲性侵得逞；隔了一周後，老公又變本加厲大玩SM，用衣服綑綁住老婆雙手，讓對方無力抵抗，再度性侵得逞。<br />\n<br />\n妻子受不了10天內二度遭到性侵，因此氣憤得打電話報警。事後先生不斷苦苦哀求原諒，妻子最後仍心軟接受，決定原諒對方並且撤告，檢方依妨害性自主罪嫌予以不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.amazonaws.com/br-cdn/temp_images/2014/02/06/98ea737b602aed84199e2f55f75be5f1.jpg?1391713428\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fbr-cdn%2Ftemp_images%2F2014%2F02%2F06%2F98ea737b602aed84199e2f55f75be5f1.jpg%3F1391713428&h=52b9314c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d26b310cd47d15c2ef4e0367a0503535bdbb89a","tid":491931,"uid":55903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"張 gif <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cf1a8b03e46affd124893a23db277c2db16126","tid":491931,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張 gif <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美式足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa89297d92a115e4fdbb2c8b480c0c7292a5c786","tid":491931,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張 gif <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=